01:08.000 --> 01:11.000
Yeah, we hired a realtor, so
She'll start looking tomorrow.

01:11.000 --> 01:13.499
I'd be happy to take her
To lunch or around the city.

01:13.500 --> 01:15.700
Oh, yeah.
That sounds great.

01:15.700 --> 01:18.300
You know, i was beginning
To think you were making her up.

01:19.000 --> 01:21.200
I'm not...making her up.

01:21.200 --> 01:24.000
Well, like i said, i'd be happy
To take her to lunch.

01:24.000 --> 01:25.100
That's good.

01:27.200 --> 01:28.200
Morning, everybody.

01:28.200 --> 01:29.900
Morning.morning.
