01:55.300 --> 01:57.100
Hello.
Wen chan.

01:57.100 --> 01:58.400
My name is hui chan.

01:58.500 --> 02:01.700
I'm wanda hoepfinger,
And this is my husband, richard.

02:01.700 --> 02:03.500
We've found it useful for both
