05:27.600 --> 05:30.100
Oh, okay.

05:31.900 --> 05:34.500
Hi. Simon griffith,
First-year fellow.

05:34.500 --> 05:35.400
You can call him
Vancouver.

05:35.400 --> 05:38.300
Oh, is that a nickname?
Not really.

05:38.300 --> 05:40.300
But you prefer it?

05:40.300 --> 05:41.100
Mmm, not really.

05:43.200 --> 05:44.200
You want to take
A look around?

05:44.200 --> 05:45.100
Hi.

05:46.300 --> 05:48.500
Hello.

05:51.200 --> 05:52.300
Oh, i'm sorry.

05:53.600 --> 05:56.600
Kate armstrong,
This is my wife, terea.

05:56.600 --> 05:59.000
Kate.
I've heard a lot about you.

05:59.400 --> 06:00.399
Oh, i've heard a lot
About you.

06:00.400 --> 06:02.200
It's so nice
To finally meet you.

06:02.200 --> 06:05.300
It is.

06:05.300 --> 06:08.400
So, what neighborhoods
Are you looking in?

06:08.400 --> 06:09.500
Excuse me?

06:09.500 --> 06:12.400
For houses.
Where are you looking?

06:12.600 --> 06:15.400
Oh, i'm just gonna
Drive around today

06:15.400 --> 06:16.700
And see what i see.

06:16.900 --> 06:18.000
Oh, great.

06:18.600 --> 06:20.399
Well, how about that tour?
You want to...

06:20.400 --> 06:21.400
Okay.
All right, excuse us.

06:28.300 --> 06:30.200
I knew we'd never make it
To ireland.

06:30.200 --> 06:34.799
I knew it, but i couldn't
Tell him to stop hoping.

06:34.800 --> 06:38.300
We stopped in new york
To see my brother,

06:39.100 --> 06:42.200
And he couldn't catch
His breath.

06:42.800 --> 06:44.300
Why didn't you call me?

06:44.300 --> 06:47.100
He didn't want me to.

06:47.100 --> 06:50.700
But he knows
He can't do much more now.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.700
You think
He'll let me operate?

06:58.200 --> 07:00.600
I don't know.
He keeps changing his mind.

07:00.600 --> 07:03.000
But i thought
It would be best

07:03.000 --> 07:03.700
If you would talk to him
About that.

07:08.100 --> 07:08.800
Okay.

07:19.200 --> 07:19.900
Hey.

07:23.600 --> 07:25.000
You look like hell.

07:25.700 --> 07:27.400
You should talk.

07:30.300 --> 07:31.400
Let me help you
Catch your breath.

07:31.400 --> 07:32.100
Yep.

07:34.800 --> 07:36.600
All right.
Deep breath, inhale.

07:38.200 --> 07:39.900
All right. Exhale.
All the way out.

07:41.000 --> 07:43.300
Again.
Breathe in as deep as you can.

07:44.000 --> 07:44.700
All right, exhale.

07:44.700 --> 07:46.100
Let it out.
Let it out.

07:51.500 --> 07:52.300
Any better?

07:55.500 --> 07:58.500
Didn't know
I'd be this afraid.

08:11.300 --> 08:12.400
What can i do?

08:17.500 --> 08:19.200
Didn't know
It'd be like this.

08:23.000 --> 08:24.900
I could admit you today.

08:25.700 --> 08:27.700
It's not too late
To put you on the list.

08:30.500 --> 08:32.000
I don't know what to do.

08:35.299 --> 08:36.100
Don't know.

08:41.600 --> 08:42.900
Why don't you let me
Help you, bart?

08:46.200 --> 08:47.400
I don't know.

09:04.000 --> 09:06.099
Okay, so this is how
The room aignment's gonna go.

09:06.100 --> 09:08.400
Mrs. Chan is gonna be
