09:08.400 --> 09:10.100
There's only one bed
In this room.

09:10.100 --> 09:11.400
We're bringing
Another one in.

09:11.400 --> 09:13.300
Because we were told
That there would be two beds,

09:13.300 --> 09:15.400
That we would recover
In the same room.

09:15.600 --> 09:17.600
There will be.
Two beds.

09:21.400 --> 09:24.400
