In the holiday inn.

09:27.800 --> 09:29.500
Yes,
After you've recovered.

09:29.500 --> 09:31.300
You'll be here
For the first three days.

09:31.300 --> 09:33.700
Excuse me.

09:34.400 --> 09:35.900
I don't feel very good.

09:42.100 --> 09:44.100
