In a minute.

09:44.600 --> 09:47.200
We need to go get some more
Blood work done now at the lab.

09:54.300 --> 09:55.900
Are they all
That bizarre before?

09:55.900 --> 10:00.700
Some. Some are really calm,
Like unnaturally calm.

10:00.900 --> 10:02.500
I couldn't do
What you do.

10:02.500 --> 10:04.400
I prefer my patients
Unconscious.

10:05.700 --> 10:07.500
You know what, though?
I think that...

10:08.700 --> 10:09.600
I don't know.

10:09.600 --> 10:11.400
I think
It's kind of romantic.

10:11.400 --> 10:12.700
A kidney transplant?

10:12.700 --> 10:15.500
The way it works.
The domino effect.

10:15.700 --> 10:18.500
I mean, a person
Volunteers their kidney

10:18.500 --> 10:20.500
To somebody that they love
Because they need it,

10:20.500 --> 10:23.100
And then if they find out
That they don't match,

10:23.100 --> 10:25.000
Instead of just giving up,

10:25.000 --> 10:29.000
That person offers their kidney
To the entire world.

10:29.200 --> 10:30.200
And then they wait.

10:31.000 --> 10:33.000
And then this happens.

10:33.000 --> 10:36.100
I mean, when somebody does that,
This is what happens.

10:37.600 --> 10:38.600
Chans or hoepfingers?

10:38.600 --> 10:41.400
Lewises.
Hoepfingers are next door.

10:41.500 --> 10:44.000
So, uh, 10 years
At st. Jude, huh?

10:44.800 --> 10:46.200
I know.
I'm ancient.

10:46.200 --> 10:48.200
Nah, you're younger
Than i am.

10:48.200 --> 10:49.500
How old are you, anyway?

10:49.500 --> 10:51.999
31.
How old are you?

10:52.000 --> 10:53.700
I am so not telling you.

10:53.700 --> 10:54.700
Hi, simon.

10:56.200 --> 10:57.100
I didn't say hello?

11:00.700 --> 11:04.100
I'm gonna go get ready
For my very important dinner.

11:07.700 --> 11:11.500
Dr. Grant's taking her out
For her 10th anniversary here.

11:12.000 --> 11:13.400
She doesn't want to go.
Oh.

11:22.200 --> 11:23.600
So, 31, huh?

11:23.800 --> 11:24.900
Yeah.

11:25.200 --> 11:27.400
Better start getting that
Retirement portfolio together.

11:27.400 --> 11:30.300
Yeah, i have a 401(k),
Some investments.

11:30.300 --> 11:31.199
I was pretty smart
After college.

11:31.200 --> 11:33.400
Simon,
I was just kidding.

11:33.400 --> 11:34.100
Oh.

11:36.100 --> 11:38.200
You know, um,

11:39.000 --> 11:40.700
Whenever there's a bunch
Of people in the room,

11:40.800 --> 11:42.600
You always have
Something funny to say,

11:42.700 --> 11:45.200
But when it's just me and you...

11:45.200 --> 11:46.400
I guess --
When it's just both of us --

11:46.400 --> 11:47.200
Yeah.

11:59.100 --> 12:00.000
Oh.

12:00.600 --> 12:04.200
Simon, um...
What are you thinking?

12:04.500 --> 12:05.300
That i like you.

12:07.700 --> 12:09.200
I-i kind of thought
You liked me, too.

12:10.000 --> 12:12.400
But, i --
Um, we work together.

12:12.700 --> 12:14.400
I enjoy your company,
But...

12:14.700 --> 12:16.300
But what?

12:16.300 --> 12:18.200
But i'm not available.

12:22.100 --> 12:23.300
Please don't tell dr. Grant.

12:24.000 --> 12:25.500
Oh, god, i hate this.

12:25.500 --> 12:26.400
What?

12:26.400 --> 12:29.700
I hate being the nurse
That's screwing the boss.

12:29.700 --> 12:30.900
It makes everybody
Look at me

12:31.000 --> 12:32.700
Like i'm either desperate
Or dangerous.

12:32.700 --> 12:34.000
Well, so, leave him.

12:34.000 --> 12:36.000
I fell in love
With him.

12:36.400 --> 12:37.400
All right?

12:37.400 --> 12:39.600
I mean, i'm not the kind
Of person that just does this.

12:39.600 --> 12:40.900
Do you think
That he loves you, too?

12:43.700 --> 12:44.600
I don't know.

12:47.600 --> 12:50.900
But i know this isn't
Gonna happen...between us.

12:52.900 --> 12:54.200
I do know that.

13:02.900 --> 13:03.900
Ms. Armstrong?

13:04.000 --> 13:04.700
Hey, mrs. Chan.

13:04.700 --> 13:07.299
I heard mr. Lewis was running
A temperature.

13:07.300 --> 13:08.399
Oh, it's very low.

13:08.400 --> 13:11.800
But even less than one degree
Above normal, isn't --

13:11.800 --> 13:14.800
Mrs. Chan, this isn't something
You need to worry about.

13:14.800 --> 13:16.600
But the risk
To the recipient --

13:16.600 --> 13:19.700
Only exists if the elevated
Temperature in the donor

13:19.700 --> 13:20.699
Is due to an infection.

13:20.700 --> 13:22.000
But i read --

13:22.000 --> 13:23.999
Mrs. Chan, we've got everything
Under control.

13:24.000 --> 13:25.900
I think you should go to
Your room and relax.

13:25.900 --> 13:26.900
Got a big day tomorrow.

13:30.900 --> 13:32.300
Everything okay?

13:32.300 --> 13:35.400
Mrs. Chan is worried
About mr. Lewis' temp.

13:35.400 --> 13:36.900
Ah, and you're worried
About mrs. Chan?

13:36.900 --> 13:38.900
I am, a little.

13:38.900 --> 13:40.400
Have you heard from bart?
Yes.

13:40.500 --> 13:42.800
Is he having a good time?
I didn't ask.

13:42.800 --> 13:44.700
You know, it's hoepfinger
We should be concerned about.

13:44.700 --> 13:46.700
Hoepfinger's fine.
He's just nervous.

13:46.800 --> 13:48.100
Mrs. Chan is on the verge.

13:48.100 --> 13:49.200
Hey.
Hey.

13:49.200 --> 13:50.800
Dr. Grant? Hi.

13:52.200 --> 13:54.400
Uh...would you be offended
If we didn't go out tonight?

13:54.800 --> 13:56.500
No, not at all.
You don't want to go out?

13:56.500 --> 13:59.599
I do, i just --
I don't feel up to it.

13:59.600 --> 14:01.500
Are you sick?
No.

14:02.100 --> 14:03.900
Look, i just don't feel
Like celebrating, okay?

14:03.900 --> 14:05.200
Okay. We won't go then.

14:05.200 --> 14:06.200
Really?
Mm-hmm.

14:06.200 --> 14:07.200
Okay, bye.

14:08.600 --> 14:09.700
Hi, dr. Grant.

14:09.700 --> 14:12.600
Hi...you.

14:13.400 --> 14:15.300
I came here
To look at houses.

14:17.000 --> 14:19.400
I got on the plane...

14:19.400 --> 14:21.500
And then somewhere over kansas,
I just realized that this --

14:21.500 --> 14:24.600
You know, it's just
A little different out here.

14:25.300 --> 14:26.700
Why did you take the job?

14:26.700 --> 14:28.200
How could i not?

14:28.200 --> 14:30.300
Head surgeon, the salary,
It allows us to do so --

14:30.300 --> 14:32.000
"us"?

14:32.900 --> 14:34.400
You did this for us?

14:38.200 --> 14:40.400
Of course. Of course.

14:41.700 --> 14:42.900
Tom, tell the truth.

14:48.200 --> 14:50.400
Truth is, terea...

14:52.800 --> 14:53.600
I don't know.

14:57.800 --> 14:59.200
I think you do.

15:03.000 --> 15:05.800
I think you knew the minute
You took the job here.

15:08.100 --> 15:09.400
I knew, too.

15:09.900 --> 15:12.500
I didn't stop you,
And, uh, i knew, too.

15:17.800 --> 15:18.900
Okay.

15:21.700 --> 15:24.300
Hi.

15:24.300 --> 15:26.100
Hey. Hey, hey.

15:27.200 --> 15:28.700
Kate,
This is my wife, terea.

15:28.800 --> 15:33.300
Terea, yeah, i know.
We've already done this part.

15:33.900 --> 15:36.400
Well,
I should actually be...

15:37.400 --> 15:39.200
It was nice
To meet you again.

15:39.200 --> 15:40.100
You, too.

15:43.100 --> 15:45.600
Okay.

