For now.

16:10.500 --> 16:11.700
Come on in.

16:12.900 --> 16:15.500
First off,
I want to apologize

16:15.600 --> 16:18.500
For being inappropriate
Today.

16:20.400 --> 16:21.200
Sit down.

16:27.400 --> 16:28.499
So, how am i doing?

16:28.500 --> 16:31.900
I can see you're beginning to be
Very comfortable around here.

16:32.300 --> 16:34.200
Yeah, i'm getting
Used to it. Yeah.

16:36.300 --> 16:39.700
Your people skills could use
Some work.

16:40.700 --> 16:41.900
Okay.

16:41.900 --> 16:43.700
I like your confidence,

16:43.700 --> 16:47.000
Though i worry that you may
Overreafrom time to time.

16:48.200 --> 16:48.999
Okay.

16:49.000 --> 16:51.500
I'm not saying that you're not
A very talented surgeon.

16:52.300 --> 16:55.900
You're just in a bit of a rush
To become a great one.

16:56.100 --> 16:57.100
Okay.

17:07.800 --> 17:09.500
What was it like
When you were a fellow?

17:09.800 --> 17:11.400
Difficult.

17:11.400 --> 17:12.299
Dr. Jacobs --

17:12.300 --> 17:14.300
Was an incredibly demanding
Chief of staff,

17:14.300 --> 17:15.699
And he put me through
Absolute hell.

17:15.700 --> 17:17.700
Yeah,
But you were working

17:17.800 --> 17:20.900
For the greatest
Transplant surgeon in the world.

17:20.900 --> 17:23.800
That's why i'm here. I mean,
That's why we're all here.

17:23.800 --> 17:25.699
For dr. Jacobs?
For all of it.

17:25.700 --> 17:28.900
Dr. Jacobs, you -- st. Jude's
Is the world's finest,

17:28.900 --> 17:30.300
And i'm just trying
To live up to that.

17:30.300 --> 17:32.600
Now, i've already been working
With the hoepfingers.

17:32.600 --> 17:33.900
Let me be your lead surgeon.

17:33.900 --> 17:35.500
Vancouver, i --
What else are you gonna do?

17:35.500 --> 17:37.700
Get one of the gut guys
From general surgery?

17:37.700 --> 17:40.600
I may be a fellow, but i'm a lot
Better than they are.

17:41.500 --> 17:43.200
Thanks for coming in
For your review.

17:43.700 --> 17:44.900
Keep up the good work.

18:09.600 --> 18:11.500
Hey. So, we're all set
For tomorrow.

18:11.500 --> 18:13.300
Great.
You okay?

18:13.300 --> 18:16.500
Why?
You look a little upset.

18:16.700 --> 18:18.400
You know what? I'm great.
And you know why i'm great?

18:18.400 --> 18:18.899
Why?

18:18.900 --> 18:20.800
Because i am totally
Getting into

18:20.800 --> 18:23.000
This whole national
"mary's 10th-year" holiday.

18:23.000 --> 18:24.999
Oh, i see.
Mary-palooza.

18:25.000 --> 18:26.100
A very mary 10-year.

18:26.100 --> 18:26.900
Shut up.

18:27.200 --> 18:29.100
Do you -- do you want to go
Get a drink?

18:29.100 --> 18:30.300
What about your date
With the chief?

18:30.600 --> 18:31.900
You don't have to
If you don't want to.

18:31.900 --> 18:34.100
You know what?
A drink sounds about perfect.

18:34.100 --> 18:34.900
Good.

18:37.300 --> 18:38.900
What are you doing?

18:39.100 --> 18:39.900
Working.

18:40.300 --> 18:41.500
Shouldn't you
Be getting ready

18:41.600 --> 18:42.900
If you're gonna make
Your dinner?

18:44.200 --> 18:46.900
Mary canceled, so...

18:47.200 --> 18:48.900
Oh.

18:48.900 --> 18:51.000
How was
Simon's review today?

18:52.000 --> 18:53.600
He's your average fellow.

18:53.600 --> 18:56.000
Right.
Don't you think?

18:57.100 --> 19:00.100
You still have
That reservation, right?

19:00.100 --> 19:02.000
No, actually, i canceled.

19:03.200 --> 19:04.600
Oh, right.

19:09.600 --> 19:10.300
Well.

19:14.000 --> 19:15.600
You could make an effort
Every once in a while

19:15.600 --> 19:18.699
Instead of sitting
In your office every night

19:18.700 --> 19:20.400
Waiting for me
To come to you.

19:23.400 --> 19:26.200
It makes me feel like
You don't really care, you know?

19:32.000 --> 19:33.300
Nathaniel.

19:37.400 --> 19:38.500
Never mind.

19:49.700 --> 19:50.900
Simon: i made a mistake coming
To st. Jude's.

19:50.900 --> 19:52.600
You know, people told me
That he was impossible.

19:52.600 --> 19:53.600
I should've listened.

19:53.600 --> 19:55.199
Mary: he's a great surgeon,
Simon.

19:55.200 --> 19:57.700
Yes, he's a great surgeon.
Mm-hmm.

19:57.700 --> 20:01.200
He just doesn't want anybody
Else to be a great surgeon.

20:02.200 --> 20:03.000
Thank you.

20:04.900 --> 20:08.500
I thought that canadians
Only drank beer.

20:08.500 --> 20:11.900
You are forgetting
Canadian whiskey.

20:11.900 --> 20:13.800
Excuse me, and whiskey.

20:13.800 --> 20:19.100
And this very special
Canadian tequila.

20:19.500 --> 20:20.800
Happy 10 years, mary.

20:21.100 --> 20:22.200
Oh, my god.

20:30.300 --> 20:31.700
Can i tell you
Something stupid?

20:33.700 --> 20:35.500
Sure.

20:36.500 --> 20:38.200
I kissed jessica.

20:39.800 --> 20:40.800
Oh.

20:41.300 --> 20:42.900
Today.

20:43.600 --> 20:44.500
Oh.

20:44.500 --> 20:46.100
In one
Of the recovery rooms.

20:49.600 --> 20:51.000
On the day
That you're asking the boss

20:51.000 --> 20:54.300
To take over
One of the domino recipients.

20:54.300 --> 20:56.000
Yes, i said
It was something stupid.

20:56.000 --> 20:57.000
Yeah.

21:00.400 --> 21:02.400
What --
What did she do?

21:02.400 --> 21:06.900
Basically, she told me
That i was out of my league.

21:08.400 --> 21:09.500
Is that what you think?

21:13.400 --> 21:17.200
I think i'm gonna have another
One of these canadian tequilas.

21:17.200 --> 21:18.100
You?

21:21.200 --> 21:23.600
Yeah. Yeah.

21:27.800 --> 21:31.000
Okay, looks good to me.
Thank you.

21:31.700 --> 21:32.500
Hey.

21:33.600 --> 21:35.000
I thought you'd be
House-hunting.

21:35.400 --> 21:38.500
Oh, well, i, uh,
Have a big procedure tomorrow,

21:38.500 --> 21:39.900
Got a lot of paperwork,
So...

21:39.900 --> 21:41.800
What are you still
Doing here?

21:41.800 --> 21:43.100
Donor hand-holding.

21:43.100 --> 21:45.200
Ah, domino donors.

21:45.200 --> 21:46.100
Yeah.

21:47.100 --> 21:48.300
Hoepfingers?

21:48.700 --> 21:49.500
Nope.
Oh.

21:55.400 --> 21:57.500
What?

21:57.500 --> 22:00.000
Are you ever going to give me
Your wife's phone number?

22:02.800 --> 22:04.900
My wife wants to leave me.

22:08.100 --> 22:09.100
Oh, i'm sorry.

22:09.100 --> 22:12.200
I just -- i don't --
I don't know what to do.

22:13.000 --> 22:14.400
Do you want her to leave?

22:16.800 --> 22:20.200
Sometimes, yes,
And then there's other times

22:20.200 --> 22:23.700
When, you know,
There's kids and houses and...

22:26.000 --> 22:27.800
We've built a life together,
So it's...

22:31.700 --> 22:33.500
It is the hardest thing.

22:36.700 --> 22:39.100
And i wish i could tell you
It was easier.

22:40.600 --> 22:42.100
Yeah.

22:43.800 --> 22:44.800
How are you doing?

22:48.600 --> 22:50.100
At first,

22:50.100 --> 22:55.100
I couldn't imagine a life
Without nathaniel.

22:56.800 --> 23:00.900
But now that
I'm on the other side,

23:01.900 --> 23:02.900
I'm better.

23:06.000 --> 23:07.200
Getting better.

23:14.500 --> 23:16.200
Good night,
Kate armstrong.

23:16.200 --> 23:17.100
Good night.

23:30.200 --> 23:31.000
Hey.

23:34.600 --> 23:36.200
Uh, can i sit down?

23:36.200 --> 23:37.400
It's the meeting room.

23:39.200 --> 23:42.000
Listen, last night,
When you kissed me --

23:42.000 --> 23:42.700
I was out of line.

23:42.700 --> 23:45.300
What you said was true.

23:46.500 --> 23:48.900
And the talking
And the flirting...

23:50.000 --> 23:51.600
I did want you to.

23:51.600 --> 23:54.000
I...just...needed you
To do that

23:54.000 --> 23:56.600
'Cause i never would have,
And then you did, and...

23:56.700 --> 23:59.900
I want you to know --

23:59.900 --> 24:02.000
I slept with mary
Last night.

24:03.300 --> 24:05.200
Wow.

24:05.200 --> 24:06.300
Yeah.

24:07.300 --> 24:08.400
Wow.

24:10.100 --> 24:11.100
Big day.

24:14.900 --> 24:15.700
Morning.

24:17.600 --> 24:18.800
Hi, dr. Grant.

24:18.800 --> 24:22.100
Hi.
The procedure's off.

24:22.600 --> 24:24.800
What? Why?

24:24.800 --> 24:28.000
One of our donors walked out
In the middle of the night.

24:28.300 --> 24:30.300
Who was it?
Kate: mrs. Chan.

24:30.300 --> 24:31.400
Well, did you try
To talk to her?

24:31.400 --> 24:33.600
We don't know
Where she is.

24:34.200 --> 24:35.100
Simon: uh, can't we call
The police?

24:35.100 --> 24:38.000
She's not a car, simon.
It's not like she's got lojack.

24:38.000 --> 24:40.400
Still,
If we can find her --
She's out.

24:41.400 --> 24:44.000
We've contacted unos and
Accessed st. Jude's database,

24:44.000 --> 24:45.500
But so far,
Nothing's come back.

24:52.800 --> 24:55.900
Excuse me?

24:56.000 --> 24:57.000
I'll do it.

24:58.000 --> 25:01.100
I'll be the donor
For the domino transplant.

25:01.100 --> 25:02.900
If i'm a match,
I want to do it.

25:09.400 --> 25:12.200
You have your anesthesiogy
And cardio evals,

25:12.200 --> 25:14.900
Tissue types, ct scan,
And you --

25:15.900 --> 25:17.200
When did you do
All of this?

25:17.200 --> 25:19.000
I've been thinking about it
For over a year.

25:19.000 --> 25:22.500
I just kind of took care
Of all the pieces.

25:22.800 --> 25:24.600
Did you know about it?

25:24.600 --> 25:26.900
We'd discussed it,
Yeah.

25:27.000 --> 25:28.700
And you're comfortable
With signing off?

25:28.700 --> 25:32.000
I am. I believe mary's doing
This for the right reasons.

25:32.000 --> 25:33.400
Is she a match for chan?

25:33.400 --> 25:35.300
No, but we're crossmatching
With a few others.

25:35.300 --> 25:37.500
How many?
Don't know yet.

25:37.600 --> 25:39.600
Could be more than five.

25:39.600 --> 25:41.900
I see.

25:42.200 --> 25:43.800
Kate, would you excuse us
For a minute?

25:43.800 --> 25:46.100
Of course.
See you.

25:47.700 --> 25:48.400
You're against this.

25:48.400 --> 25:50.000
I didn't say that.
Then you think i'm nuts.

25:50.000 --> 25:51.900
I think you might be
Caught up in the moment.

25:51.900 --> 25:54.400
So what if i am caught up
In the moment?

25:54.700 --> 25:56.900
What difference
Does that make?

25:57.000 --> 25:58.500
I'm trying
To give you an out.

25:58.500 --> 26:02.400
I don't want an out.
I...

26:02.400 --> 26:04.900
Dr. Grant, i've always been
Moved by the donors.

26:05.000 --> 26:07.100
I believe
In what they do.

26:07.100 --> 26:09.000
I promised myself
That if i ever had the chance,

26:09.100 --> 26:11.000
I would do my part.

26:11.000 --> 26:12.300
Mary, i need you here.

26:12.300 --> 26:13.500
Pam can cover for me.

26:13.500 --> 26:15.300
I'll be back full time
In two weeks.

26:20.800 --> 26:22.400
You okay?

26:22.400 --> 26:23.300
Why?

26:23.300 --> 26:24.400
It's just a kidney,
Right?

26:24.400 --> 26:25.900
It's not like i'm gonna die
Or anything.

26:26.000 --> 26:28.500
No, of course not.

26:28.500 --> 26:29.300
Okay.

26:35.900 --> 26:37.100
Hey.

26:37.900 --> 26:39.200
You sure you're okay?

26:44.300 --> 26:46.600
Bart:
Remember that congressman?

26:47.300 --> 26:48.900
What was his name?

26:49.000 --> 26:51.400
John evers.

26:52.000 --> 26:53.700
John evers, right.

26:55.200 --> 26:56.900
Altoona.

26:59.000 --> 27:00.600
Remember what happened
To him?

27:01.200 --> 27:03.900
He had i.p.f. Just like you,
We transplanted him.

27:05.500 --> 27:07.200
The disease came back.

27:07.200 --> 27:08.500
He lived
For six more months.

27:08.900 --> 27:10.400
Nate...

27:11.300 --> 27:13.400
I've made my choice.

27:14.500 --> 27:15.800
You said,
Just yesterday --

27:15.800 --> 27:17.400
Yesterday, i was...

27:19.100 --> 27:20.500
Terrified.

27:21.100 --> 27:22.800
And today?

27:22.800 --> 27:24.600
Just scared.

27:26.000 --> 27:28.000
Bart, we can --

27:28.000 --> 27:29.400
Do you remember

27:29.400 --> 27:33.000
We told him he should see as
Much of his family as possible?

27:35.200 --> 27:38.500
I was with him
The morning he went --

27:39.200 --> 27:44.100
Wife was right
At his bedside, kids.

27:44.100 --> 27:45.300
I remember.

27:47.600 --> 27:49.000
He was home, nate.

27:52.800 --> 27:53.800
Home.

28:00.500 --> 28:02.700
I want you to set up
My hospice here.

28:02.700 --> 28:03.100
Look --
No.

28:03.900 --> 28:06.400
I want you to set it up.

28:08.200 --> 28:11.000
Janet shouldn't have to be
Dealing with this stuff.

28:12.100 --> 28:15.100
I want you to do
This last thing,

28:15.100 --> 28:17.100
And i want you to see it
Through for me.

28:21.200 --> 28:21.900
Okay?

28:29.900 --> 28:35.200
I'd like to introduce everyone
To the pavels,

28:35.200 --> 28:36.300
The noahs.

28:37.000 --> 28:38.200
The farbockers,

28:39.300 --> 28:43.500
And say welcome back
To the hoepfingers, the lewises,

28:43.500 --> 28:47.200
Mr. Chan, and, of course,
You all know mary.

28:53.500 --> 28:55.000
This is gonna be
A new record.

28:55.300 --> 28:56.800
I know. Hopkins did five.

28:56.800 --> 28:58.000
That's very exciting.

28:58.000 --> 29:01.200
So, here we are again.

29:01.500 --> 29:04.000
I've made up a new list
Of surgical teams.

29:04.000 --> 29:05.900
Most of us are
On the same patients,

29:05.900 --> 29:09.300
But the big change is that
Dr. Griffith will be taking lead

29:09.300 --> 29:11.100
On mrs. Hoepfinger.

29:11.600 --> 29:14.600
Dr. Griffith, you'll use sue
And tony for anesthesiology.

29:15.300 --> 29:16.200
Okay.

29:18.200 --> 29:19.999
And, uh, take jessica
As your scrub nurse.

29:20.000 --> 29:21.300
I'm sure she'd like that.

29:25.200 --> 29:26.600
Okay, then.

29:26.600 --> 29:27.500
Tomorrow morning, first thing,

29:27.500 --> 29:31.000
We'll begin the sedation of
All six donors at the same time.

29:31.000 --> 29:32.400
Once they're sedated,

29:32.400 --> 29:36.000
The recovery teams will move
Into the o.r.s one through six.

29:48.200 --> 29:48.900
How we doing?

29:51.400 --> 29:53.700
Ah. Not exactly the week
I was expecting to me having.

29:53.700 --> 29:56.900
Yeah, i know.
New world record.

29:57.100 --> 29:59.600
I wasn't talking
About the surgeries, simon.

30:02.400 --> 30:05.000
I hope this doesn't have
Anything to do with last night.

30:05.000 --> 30:05.700
What?

30:05.700 --> 30:06.399
This.

30:06.400 --> 30:08.600
Oh, god, no.
Good.

30:08.700 --> 30:10.500
Why would you think that?
I didn't. I just --

30:10.500 --> 30:14.000
One thing has nothing to do
With the other, really. Really.

30:15.400 --> 30:16.800
Okay.
Okay.

30:16.800 --> 30:21.200
How do you feel...
About last night?

30:21.900 --> 30:23.200
I feel that it's...

30:23.400 --> 30:30.300
...awesome, what you're doing
For these people.

30:33.100 --> 30:34.800
Oh.

30:34.800 --> 30:35.800
Six-way domino transplant,
I mean,

30:35.800 --> 30:37.100
It's the first
In the world.

30:37.400 --> 30:41.000
And now you're one
Of the lead surgeons.

30:41.100 --> 30:42.600
Yeah.

30:44.200 --> 30:45.200
Well, um...

30:46.500 --> 30:48.200
You get some rest.

30:48.300 --> 30:50.500
I'll come check back
In a while.

30:50.500 --> 30:52.000
Okay.
Okay.

30:56.500 --> 30:57.200
Jessica: hey.

30:57.800 --> 30:59.300
Don't blow her off
Like that.

30:59.300 --> 31:00.399
Like what?

31:00.400 --> 31:02.500
Just now. She was hoping
You actually gave a crap.

31:02.500 --> 31:03.099
I do.

31:03.100 --> 31:05.400
Well, then stop acting like
A typical surgeon.

31:05.400 --> 31:08.300
Okay, you're the one that said
Nothing was gonna happen.

31:08.300 --> 31:09.200
You said
You weren't interested.

31:09.200 --> 31:11.200
You could've given me a day
To think about it.

31:11.200 --> 31:12.500
Now you've made things
Complicated.

31:12.500 --> 31:13.999
What, by sleeping
With the chief of staff?

31:14.000 --> 31:15.700
Screw you.
I'm just saying,

31:15.700 --> 31:18.000
I don't blame you for that,
So don't blame me for mary.

31:33.400 --> 31:34.300
How you doing?

31:37.700 --> 31:39.600
Janet's a little upset.

31:41.400 --> 31:42.500
Yeah.

31:42.500 --> 31:46.600
Not exactly happy
With the new decor.

31:48.900 --> 31:50.300
Right.

31:51.500 --> 31:54.700
So, i've, uh...

31:54.700 --> 31:56.600
I signed all the...

31:57.000 --> 31:59.000
The forms,

31:59.200 --> 32:03.700
The "do not resuscitate"
And hospice stuff.

32:07.200 --> 32:08.300
Okay.

32:10.800 --> 32:12.300
Now, listen.

32:14.700 --> 32:20.200
Make sure these folks don't do
Anything stupid.

32:21.400 --> 32:23.900
My heart stops,

32:24.100 --> 32:29.100
You make sure they don't put me
On one of those...

32:29.600 --> 32:31.100
Damn ventilators.

32:35.100 --> 32:36.400
Counting on you, nate.

32:38.400 --> 32:40.700
Make sure nobody...

32:42.600 --> 32:44.400
Does something heroic.

33:00.700 --> 33:02.700
So, the camera is gonna go
Into the --

33:02.700 --> 33:04.200
Abdominal port.

33:04.200 --> 33:06.400
Right, and then the lower
And the upper renal pulse --

33:06.400 --> 33:08.200
Will be retracted.

33:08.200 --> 33:09.500
You're a little high.

33:09.500 --> 33:11.000
Yeah.

33:11.000 --> 33:12.600
They gave me the valium already.

33:12.700 --> 33:14.700
I'm just kind of waiting
For the big stuff now.

33:14.800 --> 33:17.600
So, my renal artery,
It gets dissected.

33:17.600 --> 33:19.800
I don't really want to talk
About this. Do you?

33:20.570 --> 33:23.800
No, you're right.

33:24.770 --> 33:28.100
Hey, are we okay?

33:28.500 --> 33:30.000
It just...
It's been a little funny.

33:30.000 --> 33:31.100
How?

33:32.270 --> 33:33.600
I know you kind of like simon.

33:33.600 --> 33:34.700
No.

33:35.000 --> 33:37.100
And i know that simon
Kind of likes you.

33:37.100 --> 33:38.700
What did he say to you?

33:39.340 --> 33:41.000
He told me
That he kissed you,

33:41.390 --> 33:43.100
And that you said
That you didn't like him,

33:43.230 --> 33:48.200
But you do like him,
Don't you?

33:49.220 --> 33:52.100
No. I don't.

33:57.580 --> 34:00.500
It's been a long time
Since i've scrubbed in.

34:03.540 --> 34:04.800
Are you okay?

34:05.510 --> 34:06.500
Yeah, why?

34:06.600 --> 34:08.600
You're not talking
To anyone.

34:08.600 --> 34:11.100
No, i'm fine.

34:11.100 --> 34:12.600
Did you see bart?

34:12.699 --> 34:14.800
It's not bart.
I'm just concentrating.

34:14.900 --> 34:18.300
We're doing six surgeries
At the same time.

34:40.699 --> 34:42.900
Simon: standing by.

34:42.900 --> 34:45.300
Suction.

34:45.400 --> 34:47.000
You're giving her
Too much fluid.

34:47.100 --> 34:48.600
Man: make sure
The level stays steady.

34:48.600 --> 34:51.000
She's all right.

34:51.000 --> 34:52.900
You can't give her
That much fluid.

34:53.570 --> 34:54.900
It's fine.

34:56.239 --> 34:57.300
Vancouver,
Listen to jessica.

34:58.190 --> 34:58.800
Excuse me?

