No, no. Not on my account.
I'm...

40:35.690 --> 40:37.300
I should go.

40:44.550 --> 40:46.300
Hey.

40:51.520 --> 40:52.100
I'm sorry.

40:52.200 --> 40:55.900
No, no, no. You...
