Palliative care.

41:22.840 --> 41:24.330
I'm sorry.

41:26.150 --> 41:28.480
He's not gonna last
Much longer.

41:31.610 --> 41:32.800
Let me drive you home.

41:32.900 --> 41:34.700
No, no. I'm fine.
I'm fine.

41:34.700 --> 41:37.200
Okay. Well, we can stay here,
Have some coffee.

41:37.200 --> 41:40.900
I think
I'd like to be alone.

41:42.510 --> 41:46.100
Nate, i'm happy to drive you home.
I need to be alone,kate.

41:51.240 --> 41:53.970
I'm so sorry
About bart.

